Titolo: A Rose in the Twilight

Anno: 2017

Descrizione: A Rose in the Twilight (ロゼと黄昏の古城) is a puzzle-platform game with horror elements.  A Rose in the Twilight  was released on August 11, 2017, created by Japanese game developer Nippon Ichi Software for the PlayStation Vita and Microsoft Windows. The game is directed and designed by Masayuki Furuya.  The game's art style consists exclusively of white, black, grey, and red.

Genere: Puzzle-platform 

Valutazione: 75
